title: Google\Cloud\Bigtable\Admin\V2\AppProfile
name: AppProfile
description:
A configuration object describing how Cloud Bigtable should treat traffic from a particular end user application.

Generated from protobuf message google.bigtable.admin.v2.AppProfile

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: The unique name of the app profile. Values are of the form projects/{project}/instances/{instance}/appProfiles/[_a-zA-Z0-9][-_.a-zA-Z0-9]*.

params.name: data.etag
params.description: Strongly validated etag for optimistic concurrency control. Preserve the value returned from GetAppProfile when calling UpdateAppProfile to fail the request if there has been a modification in the mean time. The update_mask of the request need not include etag for this protection to apply. See Wikipedia and RFC 7232 for more details.

params.description: Long form description of the use case for this AppProfile.
